# ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’¼ Employee Management System (Tkinter + MySQL)

A desktop-based **Employee Management System** built using **Python Tkinter** for the GUI and **MySQL** for the database.  
This project helps manage employee records with features like **add, update, delete, search, and generate reports**.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Add new employees with details (ID, Name, Age, Salary, Department, etc.)
- Update employee records easily
- Delete employees
- Search and view employee details
- Data stored securely in **MySQL database**
- Clean and interactive **Tkinter GUI**
- Export employee details to **PDF reports** (with charts)
- Dropdown options for quick actions

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Python** (Tkinter for GUI)
- **MySQL** (Database)
- **ReportLab / Matplotlib** (PDF & charts)
- **Pillow** (for image/logo support in reports)

